ata";s:4017:"<p>Now, during this technological period, when you can develop a website for almost any business or domain, it is very important to be able to rely on a quality hosting service. And here you can encounter the same obstacles and question marks. Who can you trust? Who can you choose to take care of your business? In our case, modeltheme would not have been a successful author today on the themeforest platform if the hosting services provided by sitebunker.net would not have been 100% excellent.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><strong>What Sitebunker.net has to offer</strong></h2>\n<p>They do not just offer a virtual environment, they also take care of it. The hosting services are enhanced by their antivirus and firewall system. Your website will be given to the most capable hands, a team full of IT experts, passionate about the whole sphere of web services and <a href="https://sitebunker.net/wordpress-ssd-hosting/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>WordPress Hosting</strong></a>. You will always be kept in touch with anything that can influence your website. Sitebunker.net has a system of notifications in real-time. Customer Support is at another level, the team is dedicated to your experience, we mean, how they can host your business without being a good host.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><strong>Hosting Services</strong></h2>\n<p>Because we are specialized in WordPress themes, We`ve taken advantage of the services that Sitebunker.net offers for WordPress SSD Hosting. Although we only profit from 20% of what Sitebunker can truly offer.No matter what platform you use, whether your online store runs on Prestashop, Magento, etc., Sitebunker.net is also ready for customers like you. We know how important the crypto-coin industry is and how fast it can change. Sitebunker.net has a special hosting package for crypto-coin enthusiasts. Without proper hosting, the quality of your business is down. Good luck.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><strong>Benefits</strong></h2>\n<p>Before we started collaborating with <a href="https://sitebunker.net/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Sitebunker</strong></a>, we were a little reticent because of previous experiences.  It was surprising to learn that if we choose to collaborate with them, we will get the first 30 days of hosting, for free.</p>\n<p>For us, but we are sure that for you too, protection is very important, but more than that, the safety of your site will not suffer any losses in any way, Sitebunker offers daily free backups.</p>\n<p>On a platform like Themeforest, there will always be competitors, and because we have some fear that one day someone would be willing to try some illegal methods to hurt our progress. Sitebunker.net has our back here too. Their DDOS protection plan has left us with no worries.</p>\n<p>If you do not want to share the server with others, you can choose your own dedicated server and you will not have neighbors anymore. You can choose from the variety of promotional packages available on their website. If, however, among the packages they offer, you can not find something that suits you, you can contact them and create a personalized dedicated server just for you. What are the benefits of choosing such a dedicated server?</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ol>\n<li>The server will be released in less than 24h</li>\n<li>Remote Access</li>\n<li>Premium Software</li>\n<li>Permanent support</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>In the end, the team at Sitebunker.net is full of professionals who are proactive and know how to manage a crisis situation. Always ready to communicate in case of problem-solving. Since the beginning of our collaboration with them, we have not encountered any difficulties, and everything has gone great. We strongly recommend them with great confidence.</strong></p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://modeltheme.com/sitebunker-net-hosting-provider-review/">Sitebunker.net &#8211; Hosting Provider Review</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://modeltheme.com">ModelTheme</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:67:"https://modeltheme.com/sitebunker-net-hosting-provider-review/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:45:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:72:"How to use FREE &amp; Sponsored ICO Listings Feature in Numismatico v1.3";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:90:"https://modeltheme.com/how-to-use-free-sponsored-ico-listings-feature-in-numismatico-v1-3/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:98:"https://modeltheme.com/how-to-use-free-sponsored-ico-listings-feature-in-numismatico-v1-3/#respond";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Fri, 19 Oct 2018 11:48:04 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:9:"Tutorials";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:9:"WordPress";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:30:"https://modeltheme.com/?p=9141";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:467:"<p>The new update for Numismatico ICO Listings WordPress theme has just been released; It comes with lots of new things, fixes and improvements; Full Change Log [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://modeltheme.com/how-to-use-free-sponsored-ico-listings-feature-in-numismatico-v1-3/">How to use FREE &#038; Sponsored ICO Listings Feature in Numismatico v1.3</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://modeltheme.com">ModelTheme</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:10:"ModelTheme";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:7432:"<p>The new update for <strong>Numismatico ICO Listings WordPress theme</strong> has just been released; It comes with lots of new things, fixes and improvements; Full Change Log can be checked <a href="https://modeltheme.com/changelog-category/numismatico/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>here</strong></a>. So, let&#8217;s get started; The main feature of this update are the new <strong>FREE vs Sponsored Listings</strong> + <strong>WooCommerce</strong> <strong>Integration</strong> to checkout the Sponsored Packages;</p>\n<h3><strong>FREE &amp; Sponsored ICO Listings</strong></h3>\n<p>First of all, make sure that you have the following versions of theme &amp; plugins, as follows:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Numismatico Theme: v1.3;</li>\n<li>ModelTheme Framework: v1.3;</li>\n<li>ModelTheme Listings Manager: v1.3;</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The theme can be updated automatically by installing and using the official <a href="https://envato.com/market-plugin/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Envato Market plugin</strong></a> or <strong>manually by downloading the theme from your ThemeForest account</strong>; After upgrading the theme to v1.3 a notice will appear on your WordPress Admin Dashboard, telling you to upgrade the ModelTheme Framework &amp; ModelTheme Listings Manager plugins;</p>\n<h3><strong>Setting up Sponsored ICO Listings</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Create a WooCommerce Product; name it Sponsored ICO Listing, and set all the required options such as price, photo. etc.</p>\n<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-9144" src="https://modeltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/numismatico-ico-sponsored-listing.jpg" alt="numismatico-ico-sponsored-listing" width="1200" height="566" srcset="https://modeltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/numismatico-ico-sponsored-listing.jpg 1200w, https://modeltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/numismatico-ico-sponsored-listing-300x142.jpg 300w, https://modeltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/numismatico-ico-sponsored-listing-768x362.jpg 768w, https://modeltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/numismatico-ico-sponsored-listing-1024x483.jpg 1024w, https://modeltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/numismatico-ico-sponsored-listing-600x283.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Now, Go to <strong>Theme Panel -&gt; MT Listings Settings -&gt; Sponsored Listing Package</strong> and <strong>set the ID of the product</strong> created previously, into the &#8220;Set WooCommerce Product ID for the Sponsored package feature&#8221; field (<span class="description">Learn <a href="https://bit.ly/2RW8b0n" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>how to get the WooCommerce Product ID</strong></a></span>):</p>\n<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-9146" src="https://modeltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/step2-numismatico.jpg" alt="step2-numismatico" width="1200" height="604" srcset="https://modeltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/step2-numismatico.jpg 1200w, https://modeltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/step2-numismatico-300x151.jpg 300w, https://modeltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/step2-numismatico-768x387.jpg 768w, https://modeltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/step2-numismatico-1024x515.jpg 1024w, https://modeltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/step2-numismatico-600x302.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Set up the Pricing Tables. There will be needed two different Pricing Tables (One for the FREE Submission Package and a 2nd one for the Sponsored ICO Submission) If you just imported Demo Data, you should be able to view a new page in your Pages, named: Pricing Tables. This page contains the two tables already created by us.</p>\n<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-9147" src="https://modeltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/step3-pricing-tables-numismatico.jpg" alt="step3-pricing-tables-numismatico" width="1200" height="591" srcset="https://modeltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/step3-pricing-tables-numismatico.jpg 1200w, https://modeltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/step3-pricing-tables-numismatico-300x148.jpg 300w, https://modeltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/step3-pricing-tables-numismatico-768x378.jpg 768w, https://modeltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/step3-pricing-tables-numismatico-1024x504.jpg 1024w, https://modeltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/step3-pricing-tables-numismatico-600x296.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Sponsored Submission button should have as link something like: &#8220;<em>https://numismatico.modeltheme.com/?add-to-cart=4438</em>&#8221; where the 4438 is the ID of the product created previously. Of course, you should also replace the domain with your own domain.</p>\n<h3></h3>\n<h3><strong>How the Sponsored ICO feature works;</strong></h3>\n<p>If a customer purchases the product created (Sponsored Product &#8211; in WooCommerce), then it receives 1 Sponsored Submission slot into their account. (The slot will automatically be set if the product has been purchased by the customer).</p>\n<p>The the customer already has a Sponsored Submission slot into their account, when the ICO submission will be made, it will be automatically be set as Sponsored; This feature allows site administrators to monetize even better their websites along with the MT AdPlaces added on v1.2 update of Numismatico Theme;</p>\n<figure id="attachment_9150" style="width: 1200px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="size-full wp-image-9150" src="https://modeltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/numismatico-sponsored-listing.jpg" alt="numismatico-sponsored-listing" width="1200" height="621" srcset="https://modeltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/numismatico-sponsored-listing.jpg 1200w, https://modeltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/numismatico-sponsored-listing-300x155.jpg 300w, https://modeltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/numismatico-sponsored-listing-768x397.jpg 768w, https://modeltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/numismatico-sponsored-listing-1024x530.jpg 1024w, https://modeltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/numismatico-sponsored-listing-600x311.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">Sponsored vs FREE ICO Listing</figcaption></figure>\n<h3></h3>\n<h3><strong>Have Questions?</strong></h3>\n<p>For any presale or postsale questions you can reach us via the following mediums:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href="http://modeltheme.ticksy.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Support Help Desk (Ticksy)</strong></a>;</li>\n<li>The form from <a href="https://modeltheme.com/contact/"><strong>Contact Page</strong></a>;</li>\n<li>Via our <a href="https://t.me/joinchat/H4ioFxIrlZ4LCNEqUZe-Wg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Ofiicial ModelTheme Telegram Group</strong></a>;</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<a href="https://themeforest.net/item/numismatico-cryptocurrency-directory-listings-wordpress-theme/22448980?ref=modeltheme" class="btn-collection-theme sm btn_custom_5bfd57428d074">Get Numismatico Theme</a>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://modeltheme.com/how-to-use-free-sponsored-ico-listings-feature-in-numismatico-v1-3/">How to use FREE &#038; Sponsored ICO Listings Feature in Numismatico v1.3</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://modeltheme.com">ModelTheme</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:95:"https://modeltheme.com/how-to-use-free-sponsored-ico-listings-feature-in-numismatico-v1-3/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:51:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:22:"WordPress 5.0 Features";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:46:"https://modeltheme.com/wordpress-5-0-features/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:54:"https://modeltheme.com/wordpress-5-0-features/#respond";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Mon, 15 Oct 2018 08:19:38 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:13:"Tips & Tricks";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:9:"WordPress";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:13:"wordpress 5.0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:17:"wordpress updates";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:30:"https://modeltheme.com/?p=9023";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:197:"<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://modeltheme.com/wordpress-5-0-features/">WordPress 5.0 Features</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://modeltheme.com">ModelTheme</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:7:"Tiberiu";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:6940:"<div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid vc_custom_1539590549813"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper">\n	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " >\n		<div class="wpb_wrapper">\n			<p>Finally, after many hours of speculation and hope, the most beloved development platform will receive the new v5.0 update. Perhaps even the most important update in the last period. Gutenberg will make its appearance and revolutionize the procedures of page building. More than that, many other important updates will come out. Let`s see what are the <strong>WordPress 5.0</strong> features and how the platform will improve our work!</p>\n\n		</div>\n	</div>\n</div></div></div></div>			<div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid vc_custom_1539590554686"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper">\n	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " >\n		<div class="wpb_wrapper">\n			<h2>Gutenberg Editor</h2>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/gutenberg/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Gutenberg</strong></a> is a fresh editor that will become part of the WordPress core. With block-based functionalities and HTML customizer. All you will have to do is just click, drag and drop, duplicate blocks, edit as HTML and many other simple commands. What is great about Gutenberg is that the efficiency will improve, but the effort will be minimal.</p>\n<figure id="attachment_9123" style="width: 1920px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="wp-image-9123 size-full" src="https://modeltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/gutenberg-editor-main-view2.jpg" alt="gutenberg" width="1920" height="940" srcset="https://modeltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/gutenberg-editor-main-view2.jpg 1920w, https://modeltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/gutenberg-editor-main-view2-300x147.jpg 300w, https://modeltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/gutenberg-editor-main-view2-768x376.jpg 768w, https://modeltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/gutenberg-editor-main-view2-1024x501.jpg 1024w, https://modeltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/gutenberg-editor-main-view2-600x294.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">Gutenberg Editor &#8211; Main Post Editing View</figcaption></figure>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>For those of you who can`t give up to the classic editor when WordPress 5.0 comes out, we will teach you how to disable Gutenberg. First, you should install the <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/classic-editor/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Classic Editor</strong></a> plugin. Upon activation, this plugin will immediately activate and disable Gutenberg. Also, this plugin gives you the option to choose what editor to enable/disable. <strong>Go to Settings &gt; Writting Page &gt; Classic Editor Settings</strong> in the WordPress admin. More than that, if you decide to use Gutenberg for some time but than you realize that it needs to be disabled, you will not lose or break your website. The blocks will remain, the HTML comments are retained so that you can reactivate Gutenberg without losing anything.</p>\n\n		</div>\n	</div>\n\n	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " >\n		<div class="wpb_wrapper">\n			<h2>WordPress 5.0 Features</h2>\n<p>One of the changes in „action taking” regarding the updates will be made for the WordPress yearly update schedule. Until now you would expect two major WordPress updates per year, adding some secondary mini-updates. No more scheduled release models. The reason for that is the pressure of predetermined deadlines. We won`t get updates that fell as though but without any meaningful content.</p>\n<p><strong>WordPress will focus more on intuitive site-building experience.</strong> They are already the leaders in the market. By improving how sites are built, the team wants to keep the distance from competition that is increasing rapidly.</p>\n<p>Other WordPress 5.0 feature update will be a change to the <strong>Rest API</strong>. This feature helps developers in the process of creating products rich in functionalities. This helps when sending or pulling data from a website. Apps will be easier to develop using the WordPress platform as a framework.</p>\n<figure id="attachment_9126" style="width: 1544px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="http://v2.wp-api.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="wp-image-9126 size-full" src="https://modeltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wordpress-rest-api.jpg" alt="rest api wordpress" width="1544" height="500" srcset="https://modeltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wordpress-rest-api.jpg 1544w, https://modeltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wordpress-rest-api-300x97.jpg 300w, https://modeltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wordpress-rest-api-768x249.jpg 768w, https://modeltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wordpress-rest-api-1024x332.jpg 1024w, https://modeltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wordpress-rest-api-600x194.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1544px) 100vw, 1544px" /></a><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">WordPress REST API Docs</figcaption></figure>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Of course, a big update as <strong>Gutenberg would come with a lot of improvements</strong>. Think about platforms that sell WordPress themes. What is Gutenberg good for? To create pages. Now using the new editor, theme developing will become much more approachable thanks to blocks.</p>\n\n		</div>\n	</div>\n\n	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " >\n		<div class="wpb_wrapper">\n			<h2>WordPress 5.0 Release date</h2>\n<p>After a lot of discussions on all sorts of platforms and forums, adding a summer full of more or less true delivered information, an official date was announced. October 19 2018, is the scheduled release date of <strong>WordPress 5.0</strong>. But, this date is not a promise. The core team has also made sure they have enough space for a delay. They said: „We know there is a chance that 5.0 will need additional time, so these dates can slip by up to 8 days if needed”. Anyway, <strong>WordPress 5.0 release</strong> will happen in November. Stay tuned!</p>\n<p>Sooner or later, the update will happen and Gutenberg will become the main core page editor. This will change the fundaments of WordPress and how people interact with the platform.</p>\n<p>The WordPress 5.0 preparation progress is currently at 38% completion. According to GitHub, there are still more than one thousand issues that need to be solved. You can check the progress of the WordPress 5.0 update yourself <a href="https://github.com/WordPress/gutenberg/milestone/37">here</a>.</p>\n\n		</div>\n	</div>\n</div></div></div></div>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://modeltheme.com/wordpress-5-0-features/">WordPress 5.0 Features</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://modeltheme.com">ModelTheme</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:51:"https://modeltheme.com/wordpress-5-0-features/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:51:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:26:"Best WordPress Themes 2018";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:45:"https://modeltheme.com/best-wordpress-themes/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:53:"https://modeltheme.com/best-wordpress-themes/#respond";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Mon, 15 Oct 2018 06:54:00 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:11:"Collections";s:7: